OL,3,CFresh appeal four years after chef was
OL,4,Cstabbed to death
OL,6,FThe family of a man who was killed in
OL,7,FSheffield in 2022 have renewed their
OL,8,Fappeal for information.
OL,10,FThe body of Italian-born pizza chef
OL,11,FCarlo Giannini was found in Manor
OL,12,FFields Park on 12 May 2022 with stab
OL,13,Fwounds.
OL,15,FSouth Yorkshire Police said extensive
OL,16,Finvestigations, CCTV trawls, witness
OL,17,Fappeals and evidence gathering have
OL,18,Fyielded little information.
OL,20,FTwo people were arrested but later
OL,21,Freleased.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
