CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778775073
OL,3,CFresh appeal four years after chef was
OL,4,Cstabbed to death
OL,6,FIt's believed that 34-year-old Carlo
OL,7,Fentered the park shortly after 1am on
OL,8,Fthe morning of 12 May, but his
OL,9,Fmovements up until his death are still
OL,10,Funknown.
OL,12,FDuring the murder investigation,
OL,13,Fofficers recovered four knives at the
OL,14,Fscene, but the weapons could not be
OL,15,Flinked to Carlo's death or identify
OL,16,Fthose who killed him.
OL,18,FIn a statement issued on 12 May 2026,
OL,19,FCarlo's family said they still hope
OL,20,Fsomeone will come forward with vital
OL,21,Finformation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
